 admin123@gmail.com / 123456)\n- Start server: yarn dev  (background)\n- Wait for server to start (look for \"listening\" or \"started\")\n\n### 2. Test AUTH endpoints (PUBLIC - no token needed)\nUse curl to test each endpoint:\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/auth/login\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\", \"password\": \"123456\" }\nExpected: JWT token\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/register  \nBody: { \"email\": \"test@test.com\", \"password\": \"123456\", \"name\": \"Test User\" }\nExpected: user created\n\nGET /api/v1/auth/me\nExpected: current user info (if authenticated)\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\" }\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/refresh\n```\n\n### 3. After login success\n- Save the JWT token from login response\n- Test GET /api/v1/auth/me with the token (Authorization: Bearer <token>)\n\n### 4. Report\nFor EACH endpoint, report:\n- ✅ /api/v1/auth/xxx — HTTP status, response (truncated if long)\n- ❌ /api/v1/auth/xxx — HTTP status, error message\n\n## Rules\n- Read-only API testing\n- NEVER push or commit code\n- Kill background server when done"}],"timestamp":1776131231850,"__openclaw":{"id":"4b8eb889","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776131231877,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"5afe1e66","seq":2}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776131239731,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"55a05b1d","seq":3}}]},{"ke